0.1 Accuracy

For the accuracy responses, we fit generalized linear models (glm), using Stats R package (v.4.3.0; R Core Team (2012)).We regressed participants correct responses (1 = success, 0 = error ) on these sets of regressors [correct emotion * group * video_set + (1 |ID)] and computed significance levels for the fixed and random effects using the anova function, which returns a Type III ANOVA table with significance levels. We used Phia R package [v0.2-1; Rosario-Martinez (2015)].
